comments.body:
This has been a great discussion to see. OP in case you're interested and others find it helpful Vimeo publishes a product update feed that shows the bigger feature releases here: [https://vimeo.com/features/product-updates](https://vimeo.com/features/product-updates)

&#x200B;

We release minor improvements every week and not all of them get an article but the team here is quite dedicated to the power of video to connect people. The types of customers using Vimeo has grown over the years but filmmakers are absolutely part of the discussion. We had Ben Proudfoot (Academy Award winner for short films) come and talk to the company earlier this year about his experiences as a filmmaker and how Vimeo plays a part of that, and critically where we could do more for the craft.
